      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior still carries a deep shine, though there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and light surface scratches typical of regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all electronics and climate controls functioning perfectly. It drives smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
